<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Incorrect Wall URL</h1>
    
    <p class="mb-4">
      It looks like you're trying to access your wall using an embed token. To view your wall:
    </p>

    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside mb-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Go to your list of walls on BuzzwallHQ</li>
      <li>Find your wall you want to display</li>
      <li>Click on the wall title to find your embed token</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded p-4 mb-6">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-2">Are you trying to embed this wall?</h2>
      <p>
        If you're trying to embed this wall on your website, you'll need to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-decimal list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
        <li>Use the full embed URL: <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1">https://buzzwallhq.com/walls/embed/{your_embed_token}</code></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
      <%= link_to "Go to Walls", walls_path, class: "bg-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded hover:bg-blue-600", target: "_blank" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>